{"pageProps":{"title":"NOI Linux 2.0 上手体验 - 宝硕博客","post":{"title":"NOI Linux 2.0 上手体验","excerpt":"时隔多年，CCF 终于发布了新版的 NOI Linux ，替换了以前基于 Ubuntu 14.04 的 NOI Linux 1.4.1。","content":[{"tag":"p","content":["时隔多年，CCF 终于发布了新版的 NOI Linux ，替换了以前基于 Ubuntu 14.04 的 NOI Linux 1.4.1。"]},{"tag":"span","attrs":{"id":"more"},"content":[""]},{"tag":"p","content":["在 NOI Linux 2.0 发布的当天，我就迫不及待地下载好了镜像（",{"tag":"a","attrs":{"href":"https://noiresources.ccf.org.cn/ubuntu-noi-v2.0.iso","rel":"external nofollow noreferrer"},"content":[{"tag":"code","content":["ubuntu-noi-v2.0.iso"]}]},"），但由于时间原因，没有第一时间进行体验。"]},{"tag":"h2","attrs":{"id":"安装"},"content":["安装"]},{"tag":"p","content":["首先先新建好一台虚拟机。"]},{"tag":"p","content":[{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2021/07/25/ceaObqknR3FTtlU.png","alt":"","loading":"lazy"},"content":[""]}]},{"tag":"p","content":["新建虚拟机及挂载镜像的步骤不再过多叙述，在安装时需要断开网络连接。"]},{"tag":"p","content":[{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2021/07/25/PeYV6lquxawzL7b.png","alt":"","loading":"lazy"},"content":[""]}]},{"tag":"p","content":["开屏就是自定义的启动界面。"]},{"tag":"p","content":["安装后需要连接网络，运行 ",{"tag":"code","content":["sudo apt update"]}," 更新软件包列表，然后安装 ",{"tag":"code","content":["open-vm-tools-desktop"]}," ，安装完成后建议重启虚拟机。"]},{"tag":"h2","attrs":{"id":"简单体验"},"content":["简单体验"]},{"tag":"h3","attrs":{"id":"整体评价"},"content":["整体评价"]},{"tag":"ol","content":[{"tag":"li","content":["在考场上如果提供 NOI Linux 虚拟机的话，可能需要手动安装 VMware Tools （因为没网所以不能装 Open VM Tools），略麻烦。"]},{"tag":"li","content":["系统操作有点卡，不知道是不是因为虚拟机的原因。"]},{"tag":"li","content":["预装的软件部分是处于半残状态的，在考场上无法正常使用。"]},{"tag":"li","content":["编译器版本较新，默认支持一些新的语言特性。"]},{"tag":"li","content":["在考场上推荐使用 Sublime Text 或者 Code::Blocks 进行代码编写，不推荐使用 VSCode 。"]}]},{"tag":"h3","attrs":{"id":"更新"},"content":["更新"]},{"tag":"p","content":[{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2021/08/08/MbBrDuQyYpwP9TA.png","alt":"","loading":"lazy"},"content":[""]}]},{"tag":"p","content":["模拟考试环境时不建议安装",{"tag":"strong","content":["任何"]},"更新，以还原考场上的「本真的」NOI Linux 。如果需要日常使用则建议安装更新。"]},{"tag":"h3","attrs":{"id":"vscode"},"content":["VSCode"]},{"tag":"p","content":[{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2021/08/08/vs2mDg5KCO61n8X.png","alt":"","loading":"lazy"},"content":[""]}]},{"tag":"p","content":["CCF 预置在 NOI Linux 2.0 中的 VSCode 只能当一个编辑器，并且并没有安装中文语言包和完整的 C/C++ 扩展，处于半残状态。"]},{"tag":"h3","attrs":{"id":"sublime-text"},"content":["Sublime Text"]},{"tag":"p","content":[{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2021/08/08/TuEGMtsYcndIoNm.png","alt":"","loading":"lazy"},"content":[""]}]},{"tag":"p","content":["相比于 VSCode ，NOI Linux 预装的 Sublime Text 的自动补全功能在始终离线的环境下依旧能正常工作，同时 Sublime Text 也支持单文件编译运行，颜值也不低，写起代码来很舒服。"]},{"tag":"h3","attrs":{"id":"code-blocks"},"content":["Code::Blocks"]},{"tag":"p","content":[{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2021/08/08/J598DiCRqthEgTS.png","alt":"","loading":"lazy"},"content":[""]}]},{"tag":"p","content":["Code::Blocks 是一个免费、开源、跨平台的集成开发环境，可以在 ",{"tag":"a","attrs":{"href":"https://www.codeblocks.org/","rel":"external nofollow noreferrer"},"content":["codeblocks.org"]}," 上找到系统对应版本的 Code::Blocks 预编译二进制包及其源码。"]},{"tag":"p","content":["NOI Linux 中内置的 Code::Blocks 的自动补全、代码提示等功能均能正常使用，且不需要网络连接。"]},{"tag":"h3","attrs":{"id":"nano"},"content":["Nano"]},{"tag":"p","content":[{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2021/08/08/9BrALjlHxGK54kR.png","alt":"","loading":"lazy"},"content":[""]}]},{"tag":"p","content":["关于 Nano 此处就不再过多叙述，可以在 ",{"tag":"a","attrs":{"href":"https://nano-editor.org","rel":"external nofollow noreferrer"},"content":["The GNU nano homepage"]}," 上找到系统对应版本的 Nano 预编译二进制包及其源码。"]},{"tag":"h3","attrs":{"id":"emacs"},"content":["Emacs"]},{"tag":"p","content":[{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2021/08/08/FQdGqx8bv2oZNJL.png","alt":"","loading":"lazy"},"content":[""]}]},{"tag":"p","content":["笔者并没有深度体验过 Emacs ，所以不做过多评价，在这里推荐一篇入门教程：",{"tag":"a","attrs":{"href":"https://liujiacai.net/blog/2020/11/25/why-emacs/","rel":"external nofollow noreferrer"},"content":["Emacs 入门指南：Why &amp; How - Keep Coding"]}," 。"]},{"tag":"p","content":["可以在 ",{"tag":"a","attrs":{"href":"https://www.gnu.org/software/emacs/","rel":"external nofollow noreferrer"},"content":["GNU Emacs"]}," 找到系统对应版本的 Emacs 预编译二进制包及其源码。"]},{"tag":"h3","attrs":{"id":"vim"},"content":["Vim"]},{"tag":"p","content":[{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2021/08/08/aN9xjIneAYByEXv.png","alt":"","loading":"lazy"},"content":[""]}]},{"tag":"p","content":["Vim 还是老样子，可以在 ",{"tag":"a","attrs":{"href":"https://www.vim.org","rel":"external nofollow noreferrer"},"content":["vim.org"]}," 上找到系统对应版本的 Vim 预编译二进制包及其源码，关于 Vim 的使用请参阅 ",{"tag":"a","attrs":{"href":"http://linux.vbird.org/linux_basic/0310vi.php","rel":"external nofollow noreferrer"},"content":["第九章、vim 程式編輯器 - 鳥哥的 Linux 私房菜"]},"。"]},{"tag":"h3","attrs":{"id":"编译器"},"content":["编译器"]},{"tag":"p","content":[{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2021/08/07/lWviXCj9Txqgmr8.png","alt":"","loading":"lazy"},"content":[""]}]},{"tag":"blockquote","content":[{"tag":"p","content":["使用 ",{"tag":"code","content":["g++ -dM -E -x c++ /dev/null | grep -F __cplusplus"]}," 命令可以查看编译器默认使用的 C++ 标准。"]}]},{"tag":"p","content":["通过上图可以得出 NOI Linux 自带的编译器默认的 C++ 标准是 C++ 14 ，希望 CCF 在比赛评测的时候不要添加 ",{"tag":"code","content":["--std=c++98"]}," ，同时选手也需要做好无法使用 C++ 14 特性的准备。"]},{"tag":"h3","attrs":{"id":"对拍"},"content":["对拍"]},{"tag":"p","content":["NOI Linux 2.0 依旧安装了 Arbiter 评测系统，但是由于系统内置了 Python ，所以可以自行编写对拍程序。"]},{"tag":"h2","attrs":{"id":"后记-4"},"content":["后记"]},{"tag":"p","content":["NOI Linux 的本次更新使得 NOI Linux 系统更加地人性化、更加适合 OIer 们的使用。美中不足的一点是此版本的 NOI Linux 仍然没有卸载 ",{"tag":"code","content":["openssh-client"]}," 软件包。"]},{"tag":"h2","attrs":{"id":"参考资料-9"},"content":["参考资料"]},{"tag":"ol","content":[{"tag":"li","content":[{"tag":"a","attrs":{"href":"https://noi.cn/gynoi/jsgz/2021-07-16/732450.shtml","rel":"external nofollow noreferrer"},"content":["NOI Linux 2.0 发布，将于 9 月 1 日起正式启用！ - noi.cn"]}]},{"tag":"li","content":[{"tag":"a","attrs":{"href":"https://docs.vmware.com/cn/VMware-Tools/11.3.0/com.vmware.vsphere.vmwaretools.doc/GUID-C48E1F14-240D-4DD1-8D4C-25B6EBE4BB0F.html","rel":"external nofollow noreferrer"},"content":["安装 Open VM Tools - VMware Tools - VMware Docs"]}]}]}],"thumb":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2021/08/15/POMht9fim1vVKcp.png","date":"2021-08-08","updated":"2021-08-08","isoDate":"2021-08-08T13:44:33.000Z","isoUpdate":"2021-08-08T13:44:33.000Z","categories":[{"name":"笔记本","url":"/categories/%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E6%9C%AC/"}],"tags":[{"name":"Linux","url":"/tags/Linux/"},{"name":"VMware","url":"/tags/VMware/"}],"license":null,"permalink":"https://blog.baoshuo.ren/post/noi-linux-2/","url":"/post/noi-linux-2/","prev":{"title":"浅谈跨域资源共享（CORS）","url":"/post/cors/"},"next":{"title":"使用 Cloudflare Warp 为单栈 VPS 添加双栈网络访问","url":"/post/vps-cloudflare-warp/"},"toc":{"1":{"text":"安装","id":"安装"},"2":{"1":{"text":"整体评价","id":"整体评价"},"2":{"text":"更新","id":"更新"},"3":{"text":"VSCode","id":"vscode"},"4":{"text":"Sublime Text","id":"sublime-text"},"5":{"text":"Code::Blocks","id":"code-blocks"},"6":{"text":"Nano","id":"nano"},"7":{"text":"Emacs","id":"emacs"},"8":{"text":"Vim","id":"vim"},"9":{"text":"编译器","id":"编译器"},"10":{"text":"对拍","id":"对拍"},"text":"简单体验","id":"简单体验"},"3":{"text":"后记","id":"后记-4"},"4":{"text":"参考资料","id":"参考资料-9"}},"hasToc":true,"comments":true,"wordCount":"934 字"},"__post":true},"__N_SSG":true}